      "review_summary": "Adds a Telegram `includeGroupHistoryContext` mode across config schema, docs, UI metadata, prompt-context construction, recovered forum dispatch, and regression tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +157, Tests +255, Docs +17, Generated 0. Total +429 across 16 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the merge risk from source: latest release and current main include ambient group history for group turns, while this PR defaults unset configs to mention-only and gates ambient history on `recent`.",
